比方，你要完全把这六百万全部发完吧，感觉我们也做不到，可能公司有的部门亏损等等，去承担一些。 但是我觉得最重要的，是像这样的调改店，一年挣个两百万就行了，不要太多了，就先让它活好。 这就包括我们步步高和其他企业，包括我们在座的每个企业，调整的时候，如果企业的门店调整，现在你们最大的问题就是要活下来，然后活好，活健康，然后再去创造美好，活出美好这样的一种状态。如果是，你担心的问题，害怕员工他的那个精神上要往下滑，怎么办呢？你就他挣多少钱，70%、60%给他返还，直接每个月盘存以后直接给他当奖金发了，那他这个比说什么都好。”永辉高管谈调改，于东来直接打断！质问月赚200万为何不涨工资？"},"attached_info":"CkoIo8O67r+Hs/M9EAMaCTExNDMxMDk4MiCBmbi/BjAAOLcPQAJyEzE4OTExMDI2OTQwNTMyMTI5MzB4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"149 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-0741f2168cf72ec3daf453dab4992723_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"3_1743722944.89068","card_id":"Q_1890892421891610343","card_label":{"type":"hot","icon":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png","night_icon":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"},"target":{"id":1890892421891610400,"title":"张飞在长坂坡叫阵的时候，曹军为什么不用弓弩射杀他？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/1890892421891610343","type":"question","created":1743603884,"answer_count":49,"follower_count":95,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[44749,155094,546864,2323118,2667851],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"明明可以用弓弩拿下刘备的一员大将，曹操为什么这么糊涂呢"},"attached_info":"CkkIo8O67r+Hs/M9EAMaCTExNDMwMzA4MCCskbW/BjAAOF9AA3ITMTg5MDg5MjQyMTg5MTYxMDM0M3gAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA","detail_text":"96 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-6a6e506b2039f065c5146fea7808cb87_1440w.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"4_1743722944.89584","card_id":"Q_1890876489769132410","card_label":{"type":"new","icon":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png","night_icon":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"},"target":{"id":1890876489769132300,"ti